      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.On2ZrPJTe8FURsXY]{Operative Exploit}</p>\n<p>When you perform a @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.MBNI94tbMoqizPUk]{Trick Attack (Ex)} with a one-handed, whip-like melee weapon for your @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.bhSrjkuWxz2DQHXC]{debilitating attack}, you can attempt to @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.U37n5tY5hn1ctzQL.JournalEntryPage.R33uiOMesYP0ISWl#reposition]{reposition} the target. The target must succeed at a Reflex save or be moved 5 feet to a different location within your weapon’s reach and within 5 feet of its original placement. You can’t move the target past an obstacle. You must have the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.5hFENxRv1EN8G8ZX]{Explorer's Lash (Ex)} exploit to learn this exploit.</p>"
